This spell (which requires and consumes [[2c|money]] worth of material components to cast) gives the willing creature you touch the ability to see things as they actually are. For ten minutes, the creature has [[truesight]], notices secret doors hidden by magic, and can see into the [[Ethereal Veil]], all out to a range of 30 feet.

