!! Epic-Tier

When you cast //{{!!title}}// as an epic-[[tier|spell tier]] spell, you can cast the spell on up to two additional targets (spending 2c on components per target). Also, the duration extends to 1 hour, and the range of the truesight extends to 120 feet.

